VanishingTumblrs
================

By Pooran Prasad Rajanna

When you need this hack?

You don't want others to see a tumblr after sometime.. but forgot to delete
You don't want others to keep your tumblr clean of not so important posts
You want some of your announcement posts to always appear on top

What to do?

For destroying tumblrs after specific interval

#_10s to destroy the post after 10 seconds
#_10m to destroy the post after 10 minutes
#_1h to destroy the post after 1 hour
#_5d to destroy the post after 5 days

For reposting the post at specific intervals

#_r2h to repost the post after 2 hours so that it appears on top of your tumblr

Happy tumbling :)

Category: None

Tags: Tumblr